

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device=width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Hike Careers</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: black;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      color: white;
      font-family: 'Irish Grover', cursive;
    }

    .header {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: white;
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: start;
    }

    .logo-container {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .logo-container img {
      height: 85px;
      width: auto;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-left: 680px;
    }

    .container {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 150px; /* Adjust to avoid overlap with the fixed header */
    }

    .hike-text {
      font-size: 4rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeIn 2s forwards, moveUp 2s forwards;
    }

    .careers-list {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 20px;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeIn 2s 3s forwards; /* 2s duration with 3s delay */
      text-align: left; /* Align text to the left */
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      to {
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    @keyframes moveUp {
      to {
        transform: translateY(-20px);
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo-container">
      <a href="/home">
        <img src="/images/Screenshot (58).png" alt="Logo">
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="hike-text">Careers at Hike</h1>
    <ul class="careers-list">
      <li><strong>Join Us:</strong> At Hike, we are always on the lookout for passionate and talented individuals to join our team.</li>
      <li><strong>Open Positions:</strong></li>
      <li>1. <strong>Software Engineer:</strong> Work on cutting-edge technologies to improve our digital platforms. Requirements: 3+ years of experience in software development, proficiency in JavaScript and Python.</li>
      <li>2. <strong>Product Designer:</strong> Create visually appealing and user-friendly product designs. Requirements: Strong portfolio, experience with design software like Adobe XD and Sketch.</li>
      <li>3. <strong>Marketing Specialist:</strong> Develop and execute marketing strategies to enhance brand visibility. Requirements: 2+ years of experience in marketing, excellent communication skills.</li>
      <li>4. <strong>Sales Manager:</strong> Drive sales growth through innovative sales strategies. Requirements: Proven track record in sales, excellent leadership skills.</li>
      <li>5. <strong>Customer Support Representative:</strong> Provide exceptional support to our customers. Requirements: Strong problem-solving skills, excellent communication abilities.</li>
 
    
    </ul>
  </div>

  <script>
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
      const hikeText = document.querySelector('.hike-text');
      const careersList = document.querySelector('.careers-list');

      setTimeout(() => {
        hikeText.classList.add('visible');
      }, 1000);

      setTimeout(() => {
        careersList.classList.add('visible');
      }, 2000);
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
